OL,5, Families struggling to keep up with the
OL,6, rising cost of living are being warned 
OL,7, of the dangers of loan sharks.         
OL,9,FThe Stop Loan Sharks agency said more  
OL,10,Fthan half of victims it helped last    
OL,11,Fyear had borrowed to pay for essentials
OL,12,Flike food and fuel.                    
OL,14,FThe warning comes as UK prices rise at 
OL,15,Ftheir fastest rate in 40 years.        
OL,17,FOne woman told the BBC she borrowed    
OL,18,F#100 from a neighbour's sister and     
OL,19,Ffound herself paying back nearly #1,000
OL,20,Fa month - almost all of her pay packet.
